remarks.format: ## Remarks 可讓活動作者使用特定的簽章以公開回呼，活動使用者可據此提供活動處理常式。The enables activity authors to expose callbacks with specific signatures that users of the activity can provide activity-based handlers for. 是 ，可傳回值。 is an that returns a value. 將 的簽章指定為泛型型別引數。The signature of the is specified as generic type arguments. 有多個泛型版本這種類型，從 1 至 16 個 in 引數，加上`out`引數，稱為 「 活動。There are multiple generic versions of this type that take from 1 to 16 in arguments, plus the `out` argument, for the activity that is called. 另外還有**ActivityAction**不會傳回值的活動委派的型別。There are also **ActivityAction** types for activity delegates that do not return values.
